ends.  Anon takes care of some people, however smart people will "con" you if they are really looking for it. So, I end up hiding in lil cubbies in the bazaar and downstairs in thurgadin and never never will I sit in Nexxus and just chat again!<P>Like on of the posters above, I won't buff someone with KEI below the level necessary for C2.  I had a lvl 13 wizard come up to me in Thurg and asked for "C3" (that name annoys me for some reason) and I con'd him and said you aren't high enough for C2 and then /who all'd and said, you aren't even high enough for C1! Then I clicked my legs and gave him regular clarity.  He sends me a tell saying "if you grouped me I could get it."  I just ignored him and my husband asked why I didn't just give it too him.  Well, I'm not here to power level anyone.  I pointed out to him that with KEI, it's unlikely that wizard would have had to med for the rest of his dang level!!!<P>I love KEI, but boy it's adding to my frustration of being only good for buffing.<P>Lyden<BR>Phantasmist of Tunare
